---
import '../styles/site.css';
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logos/logo-transparent.png" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Registro | Eco Negocios e Inversiones</title>
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(232,250,235,0.88)_0%,rgba(245,252,247,0.96)_100%),url('/images/greenprojects.png')] bg-cover bg-center px-4 py-6 text-slate-950 [font-family:Manrope,Segoe_UI,sans-serif] md:px-6 md:py-8" data-page="register" data-auth-mode="register">
    <div class="mx-auto grid min-h-[calc(100vh-2rem)] w-full max-w-6xl place-items-center md:min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)]">
      <section class="grid w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/50 bg-white/75 shadow-[0_28px_80px_rgba(12,23,15,0.16)] backdrop-blur-2xl lg:grid-cols-[minmax(280px,0.92fr)_minmax(0,1.08fr)]">
        <div class="relative hidden gap-5 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(16,86,70,0.94),rgba(34,63,43,0.92))] p-6 text-white lg:grid lg:p-10">
          <div>
            <img src="/images/logos/logo-transparent.png" alt="Eco Negocios" class="h-auto w-32 md:w-40" />
            <p class="mt-5 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-200">Nuevo acceso</p>
            <h1 class="mt-3 max-w-[12ch] [font-family:'Plus_Jakarta_Sans',Manrope,sans-serif] text-3xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-[-0.04em] md:max-w-[11ch] md:text-5xl">
              Crea tu cuenta y entra al ecosistema de inversion sin rodeos.
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-sm leading-6 text-emerald-50/80 md:text-base md:leading-7">
              Activa tu perfil con un flujo mas corto y consistente desde el primer paso.
            </p>
          </div>

          <ul class="hidden gap-4 text-sm leading-6 text-emerald-50/90 md:grid">
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 text-xs font-bold">01</span>
              <div><strong class="block text-white">Alta guiada</strong><span>Completa nombre, correo y contrasena con una interfaz clara y ordenada.</span></div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 text-xs font-bold">02</span>
              <div><strong class="block text-white">Acceso inmediato</strong><span>Una vez creado tu perfil, el flujo te lleva directo al panel para empezar a operar.</span></div>
            </li>
            <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-3">
              <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 text-xs font-bold">03</span>
              <div><strong class="block text-white">Consistencia visual</strong><span>El registro mantiene el mismo lenguaje de color, jerarquia y confianza de la marca.</span></div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/15 bg-white/10 p-4 backdrop-blur-md">
            <strong class="block [font-family:'Plus_Jakarta_Sans',Manrope,sans-serif] text-base font-bold md:text-lg">Onboarding mas ordenado para nuevos usuarios</strong>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-emerald-50/80">Un registro mas corto reduce dudas y mejora la conversion antes de entrar a la plataforma.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-5 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.76),rgba(249,252,250,0.96))] p-6 md:gap-6 md:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 lg:hidden">
            <img src="/images/logos/logo-transparent.png" alt="Eco Negocios" class="h-auto w-28" />
            <p class="text-[11px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-700">Nuevo acceso</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-emerald-700">Primer paso</p>
            <h2 class="mt-2 [font-family:'Plus_Jakarta_Sans',Manrope,sans-serif] text-3xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-[-0.04em] text-emerald-950 md:text-4xl" id="loginTitle">Crear cuenta</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600 md:text-base md:leading-7">Registra tus datos o usa Google para empezar con una entrada mas rapida.</p>
          </div>

          <form id="loginForm" class="grid gap-4" method="post" action="/registro">
            <label class="grid gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-emerald-950">Nombre completo</span>
              <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-slate-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-emerald-400 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" autocomplete="name" required />
            </label>
            <label class="grid gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-emerald-950">Correo</span>
              <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="usuario@eco.com" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-slate-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-emerald-400 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" autocomplete="email" required />
            </label>
            <label class="grid gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-emerald-950">Contrasena</span>
              <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Minimo 6 caracteres" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-slate-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-emerald-400 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-100" autocomplete="new-password" required />
            </label>
            <div class="hidden rounded-[1.5rem] border border-emerald-100 bg-emerald-50/70 p-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 md:block">
              <strong class="block text-emerald-950">Perfil listo en un paso</strong>
              Al terminar el registro, el sistema crea tu acceso y prepara tu entrada al dashboard.
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="inline-flex min-h-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-teal-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-[0_18px_34px_rgba(15,138,108,0.22)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5">
              Crear cuenta
            </button>
          </form>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] items-center gap-3 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-400">
            <span class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-200 to-transparent"></span>
            <span>o</span>
            <span class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-200 to-transparent"></span>
          </div>

          <button type="button" id="googleAuthButton" class="inline-flex min-h-14 items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 48 48" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill="#FFC107" d="M43.6 20.5H42V20H24v8h11.3C33.6 32.7 29.2 36 24 36c-6.6 0-12-5.4-12-12s5.4-12 12-12c3 0 5.7 1.1 7.8 3l5.7-5.7C34.1 6.1 29.4 4 24 4C12.9 4 4 12.9 4 24s8.9 20 20 20s20-8.9 20-20c0-1.3-.1-2.3-.4-3.5Z"/>
              <path fill="#FF3D00" d="M6.3 14.7l6.6 4.8C14.7 15 18.9 12 24 12c3 0 5.7 1.1 7.8 3l5.7-5.7C34.1 6.1 29.4 4 24 4c-7.7 0-14.4 4.3-17.7 10.7Z"/>
              <path fill="#4CAF50" d="M24 44c5.2 0 9.9-2 13.5-5.2l-6.2-5.2C29.3 35.1 26.8 36 24 36c-5.2 0-9.6-3.3-11.3-8l-6.6 5.1C9.3 39.6 16.1 44 24 44Z"/>
              <path fill="#1976D2" d="M43.6 20.5H42V20H24v8h11.3c-.8 2.3-2.3 4.2-4 5.6l.1-.1l6.2 5.2C37.2 38.4 44 33 44 24c0-1.3-.1-2.3-.4-3.5Z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Continuar con Google</span>
          </button>

          <p class="hidden rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold" id="loginMessage"></p>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between">
            <a href="/login" class="underline decoration-emerald-200 underline-offset-4">Ya tengo cuenta</a>
            <a href="/" class="underline decoration-emerald-200 underline-offset-4">Volver a la landing</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <script>
      import { initLoginPage } from '../scripts/login';

      initLoginPage();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
